data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom bungalow, the perfect setting to embark on your Spokane Valley journey. Nestled within the East Valley School District, this property enjoys a prime location just a stone's throw away from K-12 schools. Convenience is key here, with the post office, grocery stores, and delightful local shops all within easy reach. Step inside, and you'll find a refreshed interior with brand new carpeting and a fresh coat of paint throughout. The addition of a new gas furnace in 2021 ensures your comfort during the colder months. The partially finished basement presents an exciting opportunity to bring your creative vision to life and further enhance this home. Don't miss the chance to see it for yourself. Schedule a viewing today and start crafting your future in this welcoming abode.
